<HEADLINE> Military Leader Visits PLA, Armed Police Troops </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NANCHANG, August 2 (Xinhua) -- China's defense minister Chi
Haotian said today that the army must exemplify late Chinese
leader Deng Xiaoping's theory of building socialism with China's
characteristics and carry on the good traditions of the Communist
Party of China (CPC) and the Chinese People's Liberation Army
(PLA).
</P>
