stopping violence in the country, on helping the Cambodian
politicians who are now abroad return home, and on ensuring a just
and free election in next May.
</P>
<P>
He also noted that he agrees with the foreign minister of
Indonesia that the return home of Prince Norodom Ranariddh at the
moment would only further complicate the problem. 
