The qualifying round saw Ashia Hansen of Britain, who rose up
strongly this year with a personal best 14.94m effort, lead the
field at 14.77m.
</P>
<P>
Rodica Mateescu of Romania, who set the year's best mark of
15.14 meters, was the second best qualifier at 14.57m.
</P>
<P>
World record holder Inessa Kravets of Ukraine, who had a quite
year this season with a 14.04 leap, withdrew at the last minute.
China's Ren Ruiping, who ranked fifth this season before the race,
didn't qualify for the final. 
