recovered by the troops, he said, adding that ground troops had
also observed over 200 dead and wounded being carried away by
the fleeing rebels.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, 4 soldiers and 10 policemen were killed and 30
soldiers injured during the confrontation.
</P>
<P>
Search and clear operation is in progress by the troops and
policemen, the spokesman added.
</P>
<P>
