<HEADLINE> American Arrested in Nigeria for Financial Fraud </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, August 2 (Xinhua) -- An American citizen has been
arrested by Nigerian authority for alleged involvement in
financial fraud, the Vanguard reported today.
</P>
<P>
